pullRequest.body:
Let `n` be a positive integer. This PR defines `BoxIntegral.unitPartition.Box` which are boxes in `ι → ℝ` obtained by dividing the boxes of the image of the integer lattice`ι → ℤ` into smaller boxes of sides of length `1 / n`.  

These boxes will be used in another PR #12405 that relates point counting in lattices and integration.

This PR is part of the proof of the Analytic Class Number Formula. 

---
